full_text.3: #USMNT’s Christian Pulisic surges forward 40 yards with the ball and curls a shot towards the far corner which is saved. Positive stuff from the American winger.
full_text.4: Christian Pulisic should have put Chelsea 1-0 up at Manchester City in the League Cup. The #USMNT forward was wide open in middle of the goal, 8 yards out, but his weak effort is deflected and saved.
